  • Packages that use IBaseInPlace 
    Package Description
    Catalano.Imaging.Concurrent.Filters
    The Catalano.Imaging.Concurrent.Filters namespace contains collection classes, which provide different image processing filters running in parallel.
    Catalano.Imaging.Filters
    The Catalano.Imaging.Filters namespace contains collection classes, which provide different image processing filters.
    Catalano.Imaging.Filters.Artistic
    The Catalano.Imaging.Filters.Artistic namespace contains collection classes, which provide different artistic filters.
    Catalano.Imaging.Tools
    The Catalano.Imaging.Tools namespace contains collection classes, which provide different image moments, analysis textures.
